<p></p>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="The_Context_of_the_verse">The Context of the verse</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=The_warning_verse&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: The Context of the verse">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<center><b>وَأَنذِرْ عَشِيرَتَكَ الْأَقْرَبِينَ</b></center>
<center><b>And warn, O Muhammad, your closest kindred.</b><sup id="cite_ref-2" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-2"><span>[</span>2<span>]</span></a></sup></center>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="The_commentary_of_verses">The commentary of verses</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=The_warning_verse&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2" title="Edit section: The commentary of verses">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="In_view_of_sunnah">In view of sunnah</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=The_warning_verse&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3" title="Edit section: In view of sunnah">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<p>According to the commentary of <a href="/wiki/Ibn_Kathir" title="Ibn Kathir">ibn Kathir</a>, Allah commands His Messenger to warn his tribe of near kindred who had very close relation with prophet and to tell them, just faith in Allah saved people. Also, this should be done with kindness.<sup id="cite_ref-3" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-3"><span>[</span>3<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="In_view_of_shia">In view of shia</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=The_warning_verse&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4" title="Edit section: In view of shia">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<p>At the verse is pointed to second step of prophet’s apostleship. Prophet is ordered to invite his nearest relations to Islam. Until that time, prophet hiddenly called people.<sup id="cite_ref-4" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-4"><span>[</span>4<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="How_to_warn">How to warn</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=The_warning_verse&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5" title="Edit section: How to warn">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<p>When prophet got this verse, he asked <a href="/wiki/Ali" title="Ali">Ali</a> to invite all relatives to <a href="/wiki/Abu_Talib_ibn_Abd_al-Muttalib" title="Abu Talib ibn Abd al-Muttalib">Abu Talib ibn Abd al-Muttalib</a>’s home and to prepare food for them. The food was a bowl of milk and a feast of mutton. Forty people of Quraysh’s elder were invited. So prophet started his warning by saying "in the name of Allah" and then invited them to embrace Islam. He said "If someone give pledge of allegiance to me, he will be my brother and closest supporter", but no one did accept except <a href="/wiki/Ali" title="Ali">Ali</a>.<sup id="cite_ref-Kaya2015_1-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Kaya2015-1"><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="References">References</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=The_warning_verse&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6" title="Edit section: References">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<div class="reflist" style="list-style-type: decimal;">
<ol class="references">
